    "description": "<strong><u>ROBODUNK</u></strong> 是 <strong>NBA Jam</strong> 和 <strong>Rogue Legacy</strong> 混在一起，加机器人。<br>天高灌篮，强力铲球和爆炸武器的<strong>扣球战斗</strong>游戏。<br>每场比赛不同的<strong> Roguelite 战役模式</strong>：即使死了，也能买下一个永久升级。<br><strong>再来……一次……灌篮！</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385890/extras/34e9a91fad17e95afab5e8eb0f3b659b.poster.avif?t=1737435898\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385890/extras/34e9a91fad17e95afab5e8eb0f3b659b.webm?t=1737435898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385890/extras/34e9a91fad17e95afab5e8eb0f3b659b.mp4?t=1737435898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>█▓▒░  <strong><u>机器人大师挑战</u></strong>  ░▒▓█<br>替代完整版的<strong>roguelite战役模式</strong>，这个序章有一个<strong>专属模式</strong>：你可以挑战<strong>机器人大师</strong>。选择你面对它们的顺序。如果赢了，你可以<strong>偷其技能</strong>。但要小心：在你每次胜利后，其它对手会变得更强大！你能打败它们吗？<br><br>●  <strong>每场比赛不同: </strong> 在有不同奖励，规则，陷阱和对手的偶然比赛选择你自己的道路。<br>●  <strong>大量解锁: </strong>特大的技能树，许多可发现的机器人模型，每一种都有自己的升级树。<br>●  <strong>养你的团队: </strong>你的机器人升级，每次胜利带来新的技能和属性提升.<br>●  <strong>收集线索: </strong>拼凑有关众神的信息，发现为什么扣篮是生命的意义。<br>●  <strong>单人和双人战役模式: </strong>朋友可以随时进入或退出.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385890/extras/06cbf3319fa73f117d722d9ed23b0553.poster.avif?t=1737435898\" width=600 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385890/extras/06cbf3319fa73f117d722d9ed23b0553.webm?t=1737435898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385890/extras/06cbf3319fa73f117d722d9ed23b0553.mp4?t=1737435898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>█▓▒░  <u>火爆的机器人运动</u>  ░▒▓█</strong><br>●  <strong>巨大扣篮: </strong> 充最大力量的跳跃，从中场起飞，在最佳时间按下以炸开篮筐。<br>●  <strong>强大的武器：</strong>猛击或使用独特的武器射击敌人，从经典的激光到从天而降的平底锅和电击环。<br>●  <strong>每轮有新模组：</strong>选择使游戏每轮不同的临时技能和升级，如二段跳、电机传球、弹药倍增等等。<br>●  <strong>危险的球场：</strong>避免或利用世界的陷阱，如尖刺滚轴、龙卷风、跳台和流星。<br>●  <strong>1到4名玩家</strong>的对战模式。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385890/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1737435898\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385890/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1737435898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385890/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1737435898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
